## Notes

- DM4b executes milestone by milestone.
- After each completed milestone, DM4b stops and surfaces:
  `Milestone NN: <name> complete; ready for critique.`
- A paired critique runs before the next milestone begins.
- The final DM4b critique is the end-to-end performance-analysis
  gate after all milestones are complete.
